俾稅局個數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T03:31:07.000Z","msg":"上市公司份年報會寫年薪， 佢個價以主席黎講其實好少，不過佢係大股東，個數只不過係帳面數黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  另外花紅好似唔洗寫落年報到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753c31aa5e5d6f4d4989683a9b9b73c1a848d97d","tid":745560,"uid":82917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T04:42:30.000Z","msg":"唔買豪宅嫁黎把撚呀？？"},{"pid":"bf0e3a06cdb4eedb58b2b13da4fef7f4ec96a6ad","tid":745560,"uid":92690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T04:53:27.000Z","msg":"兩姐妹都係俾佢老母調較做嫁人豪門機器<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7a479f2b1657c0c2fd96713184a030f1fdf0f7","tid":745560,"uid":192808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:00:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d71983b426c7c8b6af814a64210c2ec9a50300af","tid":745560,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"753c31aa5e5d6f4d4989683a9b9b73c1a848d97d","tid":745560,"uid":82917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T04:42:30.000Z","msg":"唔買豪宅嫁黎把撚呀？？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:37:24.000Z","msg":"係呀，係以前．．．以前．．．費事嘈呀．．．"},{"pid":"6bc86b013b71b0a088db4c214eb94619279554c4","tid":745560,"uid":17545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d71983b426c7c8b6af814a64210c2ec9a50300af","tid":745560,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"753c31aa5e5d6f4d4989683a9b9b73c1a848d97d","tid":745560,"uid":82917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T04:42:30.000Z","msg":"唔買豪宅嫁黎把撚呀？？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:37:24.000Z","msg":"係呀，係以前．．．以前．．．費事嘈呀．．．"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我幢二百億既the one"},{"pid":"205984284eead60dfd0a29d35be4df9d52a77164","tid":745560,"uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6bc86b013b71b0a088db4c214eb94619279554c4","tid":745560,"uid":17545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d71983b426c7c8b6af814a64210c2ec9a50300af","tid":745560,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"753c31aa5e5d6f4d4989683a9b9b73c1a848d97d","tid":745560,"uid":82917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T04:42:30.000Z","msg":"唔買豪宅嫁黎把撚呀？？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:37:24.000Z","msg":"係呀，係以前．．．以前．．．費事嘈呀．．．"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我幢二百億既the one"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:14:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">李嘉欣不是The ONE</span><br />\n<br />\n李嘉欣曾經是劉鑾雄生命中的一個女人，大劉名下華人置業於02年斥資11.06億元買入位於尖沙嘴的東英大廈，06年拆卸後重建，同年大劉以「The ONE」的署名，在報章刊登全版廣告，高調賀舊愛嘉欣於6月20日生日快樂，並寫着「With love」寄意，由於當年嘉欣和許晉亨拍拖，這份生日廣告轟動一時。<br />\n<br />\n09年大劉將東英大廈易名為「The ONE」，有指是為08年成為許太的嘉欣送上生日禮物，情深義重。當年大劉兒子劉鳴煒出席「The ONE」命名儀式記者會時，被問到名字是否意有所指？他尷尬表示是揀一個簡單、直接、易記的名字。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/181309_dab2568a6ab4c95380350431be658ec8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F181309_dab2568a6ab4c95380350431be658ec8.png&h=b0b01c87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大劉無諗住送畀你，佢登廣告來把撚呀！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9cbf2db9cbec25f63c8c93637aac22ee55979c","tid":745560,"uid":74858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6b8a33d157fb1edf64d66f07ecbe0c1d118fbba","tid":745560,"uid":137694,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"d8201869a83029bea8c2e0bcb26fe1734369c464","tid":745560,"uid":83328,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T01:24:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/091744_299de81c16166db0524b55b71f57a273.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F091744_299de81c16166db0524b55b71f57a273.gif&h=10870932&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好心爛果唔好咁仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T03:01:55.000Z","msg":"年薪98萬都打出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:35:24.000Z","msg":"仲要笑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地股息都唔只<br />\n不嬲呢d 都報得好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a55e13d55449118b6b07a75ba47ba1a4910098d","tid":745560,"uid":192808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:35:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1160d6c74969cab969588e5bceaafdeb9f10984e","tid":745560,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a9cbf2db9cbec25f63c8c93637aac22ee55979c","tid":745560,"uid":74858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6b8a33d157fb1edf64d66f07ecbe0c1d118fbba","tid":745560,"uid":137694,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"d8201869a83029bea8c2e0bcb26fe1734369c464","tid"